<topic title="Card view page">
	<section title="What you can do on this page">
		<p>
			The Card view page lets you view details for a card including all properties attached to this card. 
			From here you can add tags, edit card descriptions and change card properties. 
			If you have card transition(s) setup that match the card properties, you can also 'transition' this card to the next stage of its life cycle (i.e. update multiple properties at once).
